air) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37746,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/03\/14\/shukr-sabr-sawm\/","url_meta":{"origin":42319,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Gratitude: Thankfulness to Allah rewarded like patience","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 14, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Sinan ibn Sannah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe one who eats gratefully has a reward similar to one who fasts patiently.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 1765 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0633\u0650\u0646\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0633\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0629\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0623\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0644\u064e\u0645\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32896,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/27\/charity-from-haram-wealth\/","url_meta":{"origin":42319,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Zakat: Charity from unlawful wealth is not rewarded","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 27, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upo